@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bhaltu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(v0)
    v0 = wp.exp((v2 - (tmp + 0.66 - v0 + 0.35)))
    v2 = wp.sin((v1 * v0))
    v2 = 0.12
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.35)))
    data[tid] = v0
